1
00:00:06,834 --> 00:00:11,271
<i>We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high</i>

2
00:00:11,439 --> 00:00:14,966
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>don't care what people think about them</i>

3
00:00:15,042 --> 00:00:18,478
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>follow what they believe</i>

4
00:00:18,546 --> 00:00:22,141
<i>Oli Oli Oli Oh! Just go my way</i>

5
00:00:22,216 --> 00:00:25,481
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

6
00:00:25,553 --> 00:00:27,487
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>

7
00:00:29,290 --> 00:00:32,225
<i>Down a difficult road</i>
<i>filled with endless struggles</i>

8
00:00:32,293 --> 00:00:36,093
<i>Where do you think you are going</i>
<i>following someone else's map?</i>

9
00:00:36,497 --> 00:00:43,335
<i>An insightful crow comes along</i>
<i>to tear up the map</i>

10
00:00:43,571 --> 00:00:50,636
<i>Now open your eyes and</i>
<i>take a look at the truth (Yeah!)</i>

11
00:00:50,945 --> 00:00:57,077
<i>There's nothing to lose,</i>
<i>so let's GO!!!</i>

12
00:00:57,218 --> 00:01:01,484
<i>We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high</i>

13
00:01:01,555 --> 00:01:05,150
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>don't care what people think about them</i>

14
00:01:05,226 --> 00:01:08,559
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>follow what they believe</i>

15
00:01:08,629 --> 00:01:12,258
<i>Oli Oli Oli Oh!</i>
<i>Just go my way</i>

16
00:01:12,333 --> 00:01:15,928
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

17
00:01:16,003 --> 00:01:19,495
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best!</i>

18
00:01:19,573 --> 00:01:23,168
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

19
00:01:23,244 --> 00:01:27,340
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best! BANG!</i>

20
00:01:37,369 --> 00:01:43,035
Hey, Pervy Sage. What Jutsu are you
gonna teach me this time?

21
00:01:43,408 --> 00:01:48,675
The last time was Walk on Water Jutsu,
so is it gonna be Walk on Fire Jutsu?

22
00:01:49,614 --> 00:01:52,811
Or maybe Walk in the Air?

23
00:01:54,452 --> 00:01:57,546
Hurry up and tell me, Pervy Sage!

24
00:01:58,456 --> 00:02:01,391
You keep calling me Pervy Sage.

25
00:02:01,459 --> 00:02:04,485
So you have no idea that
I'm a superb person, huh?

26
00:02:04,562 --> 00:02:07,053
Huh...? A superb Pervy Sage?

27
00:02:08,600 --> 00:02:10,534
Nhaagh... Listen carefully!

28
00:02:12,537 --> 00:02:15,097
Toad Sage is only a disguise!

29
00:02:16,207 --> 00:02:19,643
As a matter of fact...!

30
00:02:20,712 --> 00:02:23,044
North and South and East and West!

31
00:02:24,582 --> 00:02:26,243
I'm the white maned toad charmer,

32
00:02:26,318 --> 00:02:29,981
and one of the legendary Sannin whom
even celestial beings can't defeat.

33
00:02:30,055 --> 00:02:31,249
Such a stud!

34
00:02:31,323 --> 00:02:33,257
That he strikes fear...
in the hearts of people!

35
00:02:33,325 --> 00:02:35,816
I am no other than "Master Jiraiya"!

36
00:02:37,128 --> 00:02:42,122
Yes...
I'm talking about me!

37
00:02:44,069 --> 00:02:45,127
Huh...

38
00:03:03,355 --> 00:03:09,191
<i>Jiraiya.</i>
<i>Naruto's Potential Disaster</i>

39
00:03:14,866 --> 00:03:18,893
Atafuku Town?
That's ten kilometers from here!

40
00:03:18,970 --> 00:03:21,165
It's "O" tafuku Town!

41
00:03:21,706 --> 00:03:25,267
Hey... hey...
Hey, Pervy Sage!

42
00:03:26,244 --> 00:03:29,736
I'm telling you, it's Jiraiya.
Gimme a break...

43
00:03:30,014 --> 00:03:32,141
So the fact that such
a bigwig Pervy Sage like you

44
00:03:32,217 --> 00:03:35,812
is taking me along as
his travel companion means...

45
00:03:35,887 --> 00:03:39,084
that I'm potentially a genius?

46
00:03:39,157 --> 00:03:40,522
Just as I thought!

47
00:03:44,095 --> 00:03:46,655
Hey! Hey! Hey!
Why did you choose me?

48
00:03:49,167 --> 00:03:53,968
A long time ago
the Fourth Hokage was my disciple.

49
00:03:56,241 --> 00:04:00,701
And you resemble the Fourth Hokage
so much, it's almost funny.

50
00:04:00,945 --> 00:04:04,176
That's the only reason...

51
00:04:05,116 --> 00:04:06,481
I...?

52
00:04:07,752 --> 00:04:09,481
The Fourth Hokage...?

53
00:04:12,056 --> 00:04:13,318
Yeah!

54
00:04:13,391 --> 00:04:14,790
Yeah! Yeah!

55
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:16,422
W-What is it?

56
00:04:17,061 --> 00:04:18,358
Yeah!

57
00:04:18,997 --> 00:04:21,090
The fact that I resemble
the Fourth Hokage means

58
00:04:21,166 --> 00:04:23,566
that I also possess genius
of his level, right?

59
00:04:23,635 --> 00:04:27,036
I'll become the Hokage, after all!
All right!

60
00:04:35,413 --> 00:04:37,506
W-Wait...

61
00:04:42,187 --> 00:04:43,654
I stepped on some dog poop!

62
00:04:47,025 --> 00:04:49,323
About the only areas you resemble
the Fourth Hokage

63
00:04:49,394 --> 00:04:51,954
are your hair and your stubbornness!

64
00:04:52,797 --> 00:04:55,698
What was that?!
You senile Pervy Sage!

65
00:04:57,202 --> 00:04:58,635
Not again!

66
00:05:13,718 --> 00:05:15,709
Sakura? Come here!

67
00:05:16,087 --> 00:05:16,985
Okay!

68
00:05:17,622 --> 00:05:20,090
Please take these rice sweets
over to Ino's house.

69
00:05:20,725 --> 00:05:22,090
Ino's house?

70
00:05:22,927 --> 00:05:23,586
These?

71
00:05:23,661 --> 00:05:24,753
That's right...

72
00:05:25,497 --> 00:05:28,057
Don't bother them
by staying too long.

73
00:05:28,132 --> 00:05:29,963
Because everyone is
very busy at this time.

74
00:05:30,602 --> 00:05:32,069
I know that!

75
00:05:32,136 --> 00:05:33,694
See you later!

76
00:05:39,811 --> 00:05:41,005
Oh, yeah...

77
00:05:41,079 --> 00:05:43,639
I'll bring some over
to Sasuke later on too.

78
00:05:44,115 --> 00:05:45,673
I wonder if he likes sweets...?

79
00:05:46,484 --> 00:05:48,418
And to Naruto too...

80
00:05:48,486 --> 00:05:50,886
Naruto looks like
he would eat anything...

81
00:05:55,159 --> 00:05:58,253
Hey Kakashi Sensei!
Teach me Chidori too!

82
00:05:58,630 --> 00:06:02,566
You may say teach me,
but it's not that easy.

83
00:06:02,634 --> 00:06:03,931
What the heck's that?!

84
00:06:04,002 --> 00:06:06,027
That's not fair, show me how!
Teach it to me.

85
00:06:06,971 --> 00:06:09,235
Sasuke... Thank you...

86
00:06:09,974 --> 00:06:13,603
You rescued me from
the Sand Ninja, right?

87
00:06:16,447 --> 00:06:17,379
No...

88
00:06:17,448 --> 00:06:18,540
Huh?

89
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:25,583
For a start, why don't you try gathering
Chakra in your palms!

90
00:06:25,657 --> 00:06:26,954
All right!

91
00:06:29,060 --> 00:06:32,894
The person who rescued you...
was Naruto.

92
00:06:35,266 --> 00:06:37,826
Like this? Like this?

93
00:06:38,369 --> 00:06:42,032
Oh come on, Sasuke,
you're being overmodest again.

94
00:06:43,141 --> 00:06:46,508
It's true that Naruto has gotten stronger,
but against that Sand Ninja...

95
00:06:46,578 --> 00:06:48,045
I'm telling you the truth.

96
00:06:52,517 --> 00:06:57,181
That kid fought desperately
to rescue you.

97
00:06:58,122 --> 00:07:00,750
He showed a kind of strength that
he had never shown before.

98
00:07:02,126 --> 00:07:06,688
Naruto rescued... me.

99
00:07:10,535 --> 00:07:12,696
Oh, it's coming...

100
00:07:13,371 --> 00:07:20,209
Chidori! Huh? Chidori! Chidori!

101
00:07:22,213 --> 00:07:24,943
All right! I'll bring some to Naruto too!

102
00:07:40,965 --> 00:07:45,698
<i>I wasn't...</i>
<i>I wasn't able to do anything...</i>

103
00:07:46,971 --> 00:07:54,173
<i>I don't want to watch a precious comrade</i>
<i>die right before my eyes ever again...</i>

104
00:07:56,114 --> 00:08:02,781
<i>No matter what,</i>
<i>I will protect you!</i>

105
00:08:03,688 --> 00:08:06,156
<i>Multi Shadow Clone Jutsu!</i>

106
00:08:12,964 --> 00:08:14,556
<i>Summoning Jutsu!</i>

107
00:08:24,308 --> 00:08:27,141
<i>Naruto is getting stronger and stronger.</i>

108
00:08:28,613 --> 00:08:31,343
<i>Compared to him, I...</i>

109
00:08:51,969 --> 00:08:54,904
While you may able to
manage against him,

110
00:08:54,972 --> 00:08:57,167
I couldn't possibly...

111
00:08:58,009 --> 00:08:59,738
He's in a completely different level...

112
00:09:00,211 --> 00:09:01,371
Yeah...

113
00:09:01,446 --> 00:09:04,973
If we go at each other,
we'll either both be killed or at best,

114
00:09:05,049 --> 00:09:07,677
kill each other simultaneously.

115
00:09:08,252 --> 00:09:12,348
Even if we increased the numbers,
that wouldn't change

116
00:09:12,724 --> 00:09:16,182
I didn't expect the kid's guard
would be a legendary Sannin.

117
00:09:16,828 --> 00:09:18,295
With him as the opponent...

118
00:09:18,362 --> 00:09:20,830
the names of Leaf Village's Uchiha Clan

119
00:09:20,898 --> 00:09:25,028
and the Seven Ninja Swordsmen
of Mist would be tarnished.

120
00:09:25,603 --> 00:09:27,594
Yeah. However...

121
00:09:28,339 --> 00:09:32,435
Any strong one has a weakness...

122
00:09:48,460 --> 00:09:50,985
Stop! You will get cursed!

123
00:09:54,299 --> 00:09:56,426
Hey, hey, Pervy Sage...

124
00:09:56,501 --> 00:09:57,661
Huh?!

125
00:09:58,136 --> 00:10:00,696
What kind of a student was
the Fourth Hokage?

126
00:10:01,006 --> 00:10:02,496
Well, I guess one could say

127
00:10:02,574 --> 00:10:05,008
that he developed to that extent
because he was my student...

128
00:10:05,077 --> 00:10:09,173
You're one lucky guy
to be taught by me!

129
00:10:10,382 --> 00:10:12,373
- Hmmm...
- Hmmm...

130
00:10:12,918 --> 00:10:14,408
Are you dubious?

131
00:10:14,486 --> 00:10:16,750
A good teacher will develop
good disciples.

132
00:10:16,822 --> 00:10:18,517
That goes without saying.

133
00:10:18,623 --> 00:10:22,889
Then, then, who taught you,
Pervy Sage?

134
00:10:22,961 --> 00:10:24,258
Me?

135
00:10:24,329 --> 00:10:26,923
I learned from the Third Hokage.

136
00:10:26,999 --> 00:10:28,364
The Third Hokage?

137
00:10:28,834 --> 00:10:29,994
That's right...

138
00:10:30,068 --> 00:10:33,560
The Third Hokage was
still young and lively.

139
00:10:33,939 --> 00:10:36,669
- The Third Hokage... young and lively?
- The Third Hokage... young and lively?

140
00:10:37,242 --> 00:10:40,700
That's right!
I was young and lively too!

141
00:10:41,346 --> 00:10:42,711
Young and lively?!

142
00:10:50,188 --> 00:10:52,179
I... I got tangled up.

143
00:10:52,391 --> 00:10:54,951
See... You got cursed...

144
00:10:57,229 --> 00:10:59,789
So you learned from Kakashi.

145
00:10:59,865 --> 00:11:02,891
Then you experienced
the "Bell Training," right?

146
00:11:03,268 --> 00:11:04,098
Huh?

147
00:11:04,169 --> 00:11:07,002
Yeah! I did! Yes I did!

148
00:11:16,515 --> 00:11:20,246
Only I was tied to the tree trunk
and had one deuce of a time...

149
00:11:20,619 --> 00:11:22,712
What? You too?

150
00:11:22,788 --> 00:11:24,278
Huh? What do you mean
by "you too"?

151
00:11:24,356 --> 00:11:25,084
Huh?

152
00:11:25,157 --> 00:11:26,215
What do you mean by "you too"?

153
00:11:26,291 --> 00:11:29,385
Why don't you just hurry,
get up and return those things.

154
00:11:29,828 --> 00:11:32,922
Even if you were to say that...
it's pretty difficult...

155
00:11:38,136 --> 00:11:39,797
There are two bells.

156
00:11:39,871 --> 00:11:42,066
The fact that there are
only two means...

157
00:11:42,174 --> 00:11:44,165
That one of us has to go
to the tree trunk...

158
00:11:44,709 --> 00:11:47,007
You're quick on the uptake, Orochimaru.

159
00:11:47,479 --> 00:11:50,004
All right! I'll make it!

160
00:11:50,882 --> 00:11:53,578
Come at me with the intent to kill!

161
00:12:05,831 --> 00:12:08,925
Jiraiya, I won the bet with you, didn't I?

162
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:11,560
You got tied to the tree trunk,
after all.

163
00:12:11,636 --> 00:12:12,660
Shut up!

164
00:12:12,737 --> 00:12:14,671
You flat chested like a cutting board.

165
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:18,141
What did you say?!
You nerdy perv!

166
00:12:19,444 --> 00:12:22,277
Okay, Okay, that's enough.

167
00:12:22,347 --> 00:12:24,212
Tsunade and Orochimaru go home!

168
00:12:24,282 --> 00:12:25,271
Okay!

169
00:12:37,262 --> 00:12:39,526
You are hopeless...

170
00:12:39,698 --> 00:12:44,260
Ninja shouldn't be getting caught in
obvious traps like that over and over again.

171
00:12:44,336 --> 00:12:45,462
But...

172
00:12:45,537 --> 00:12:47,732
Why don't you learn a little
from Orochimaru?!

173
00:12:48,740 --> 00:12:52,506
Sarutobi Sensei, you're always
saying Orochimaru, Orochimaru!

174
00:12:52,777 --> 00:12:53,766
Hm?

175
00:12:54,012 --> 00:12:58,142
When it comes to snooping,
I'm really good at Transparency Jutsu.

176
00:12:59,084 --> 00:13:00,244
Gimme a break...

177
00:13:00,318 --> 00:13:02,081
I don't even wanna know

178
00:13:02,154 --> 00:13:03,382
what level of Transparency Jutsu
you possess...

179
00:13:03,455 --> 00:13:07,118
I've never been caught once!
And that's the truth!

180
00:13:08,393 --> 00:13:13,854
If you're that sure of yourself,
I'll go with you next time...

181
00:13:17,636 --> 00:13:20,002
You're such a lecher, Sarutobi Sensei...

182
00:13:23,642 --> 00:13:25,109
Huh?! Huh?

183
00:13:26,211 --> 00:13:27,303
What, what?

184
00:13:27,846 --> 00:13:28,471
Hey!

185
00:13:28,547 --> 00:13:30,674
What's so funny?! Pervy Sage!

186
00:13:30,749 --> 00:13:31,681
Huh?

187
00:13:31,750 --> 00:13:35,618
It's just as I said, a good teacher
will develop good disciples.

188
00:13:36,254 --> 00:13:38,950
Huh...? I don't understand
what you're saying!

189
00:13:39,024 --> 00:13:41,754
Come on, let's go.
Did you put it back properly?

190
00:13:41,826 --> 00:13:43,555
Yeah, I fixed them!

191
00:13:47,499 --> 00:13:48,397
See!

192
00:14:05,483 --> 00:14:09,681
It appears that they haven't
found Naruto yet.

193
00:14:09,854 --> 00:14:12,789
But don't you think that's strange!?

194
00:14:13,825 --> 00:14:16,988
Those guys had already
infiltrated the village.

195
00:14:17,362 --> 00:14:19,990
It should be easy to find Naruto
in this village.

196
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:24,935
Itachi knows Naruto's face.

197
00:14:26,705 --> 00:14:28,036
Kakashi...

198
00:14:33,078 --> 00:14:35,069
Why is Kakashi sleeping?

199
00:14:35,247 --> 00:14:37,181
Besides, only Jonin are gathering here...

200
00:14:37,449 --> 00:14:40,009
What are you doing?
What in the world happened?!

201
00:14:40,185 --> 00:14:42,949
Nothing... in particular...

202
00:14:43,021 --> 00:14:45,649
Is it true that that
Itachi has returned?!

203
00:14:47,492 --> 00:14:49,426
And moreover,
that he's after Naruto?!

204
00:14:53,765 --> 00:14:54,697
Oh...

205
00:14:55,734 --> 00:14:56,894
Idiot...

206
00:15:03,108 --> 00:15:05,099
Why does this always happen?!

207
00:15:11,983 --> 00:15:16,443
<i>So that guy returned to this village?</i>
<i>And moreover, he's pursuing Naruto?</i>

208
00:15:16,521 --> 00:15:17,818
<i>What does all this mean?!</i>

209
00:15:27,866 --> 00:15:28,764
Sasuke?!

210
00:15:28,833 --> 00:15:29,959
Where's Naruto?!

211
00:15:30,035 --> 00:15:32,697
Huh? I just got here too.

212
00:15:33,071 --> 00:15:34,902
I wanted to give Naruto...

213
00:15:35,240 --> 00:15:36,172
Some sweets...?

214
00:15:36,541 --> 00:15:38,736
<i>If Naruto is caught by that guy,</i>
<i>that will spell his end.</i>

215
00:15:40,645 --> 00:15:42,374
<i>I'm not gonna let him do that!</i>

216
00:15:43,114 --> 00:15:45,844
Hey old man!
Naruto must have come here!

217
00:15:46,217 --> 00:15:48,515
And do you know
where he went after that?

218
00:15:48,787 --> 00:15:50,618
Oh, Naruto, right...

219
00:15:50,889 --> 00:15:52,652
If I remember correctly...

220
00:15:53,625 --> 00:15:55,820
Master Jiraiya came here
around noon and...

221
00:15:56,628 --> 00:16:00,462
They ate ramen together,
and he said he was going somewhere...

222
00:16:00,665 --> 00:16:01,359
Where?!

223
00:16:01,900 --> 00:16:06,735
Hmm... I think he said to a post station
some distance from the village...

224
00:16:08,973 --> 00:16:11,373
And then he left with Master Jiraiya.

225
00:16:11,876 --> 00:16:12,865
Jiraiya?

226
00:16:14,079 --> 00:16:17,071
Jiraiya - one of the genius Sannin.

227
00:16:17,749 --> 00:16:19,842
Well, in appearance,

228
00:16:19,918 --> 00:16:22,443
he just looks like
a big white haired old man.

229
00:16:22,987 --> 00:16:25,319
Big and white-haired...

230
00:16:26,524 --> 00:16:27,786
H-Hey!

231
00:16:28,259 --> 00:16:31,353
Geez... If you're gonna
ask somebody a question,

232
00:16:31,429 --> 00:16:33,522
it's only polite to stay
and have a ramen or something.

233
00:16:46,778 --> 00:16:48,336
Candies are here.

234
00:16:54,719 --> 00:16:57,813
This town is pretty weird.

235
00:17:14,105 --> 00:17:15,470
Naruto!

236
00:17:15,540 --> 00:17:16,370
Huh?

237
00:17:16,441 --> 00:17:18,204
We're staying here tonight!

238
00:17:18,443 --> 00:17:21,310
What?! I can still walk!

239
00:17:21,679 --> 00:17:23,874
A disciple should obey his master!

240
00:17:24,315 --> 00:17:26,442
I just want to learn the Jutsu!

241
00:17:26,951 --> 00:17:28,976
That's what's called a disciple!

242
00:17:29,354 --> 00:17:30,252
Huh?!

243
00:17:40,532 --> 00:17:43,296
Oh, oh...!

244
00:17:49,274 --> 00:17:50,673
Naruto!

245
00:17:51,142 --> 00:17:51,904
Yes?

246
00:17:53,478 --> 00:17:55,002
Here, this is the key to the room.

247
00:17:55,079 --> 00:17:56,637
Go to the room ahead of me,
practice Chakra,

248
00:17:56,815 --> 00:17:58,146
train some and go to sleep!

249
00:17:58,216 --> 00:17:59,046
Got it?!

250
00:17:59,117 --> 00:18:00,049
What?!

251
00:18:00,118 --> 00:18:02,586
"The adult world is gonna begin
from this point on"...

252
00:18:02,654 --> 00:18:05,054
Is that the vibe, Pervy Sage?!
That's not fair!

253
00:18:05,990 --> 00:18:08,515
That post town isn't that far...!

254
00:18:11,830 --> 00:18:15,459
This! Somehow this always happens
when I'm with that Pervy Sage!

255
00:18:19,237 --> 00:18:20,067
Darn...

256
00:18:21,773 --> 00:18:22,865
Here...

257
00:18:30,281 --> 00:18:31,748
Candies are here!

258
00:18:35,019 --> 00:18:36,714
I've got to check door by door!

259
00:18:37,755 --> 00:18:38,949
Cheers!

260
00:18:40,091 --> 00:18:43,322
I wonder if he really has any inclination
to oversee my training?

261
00:18:52,637 --> 00:18:54,400
What about that one? Yeah that.

262
00:18:58,042 --> 00:19:00,408
See! A hundred out of a hundred!

263
00:19:01,045 --> 00:19:04,139
Do you have a blonde kid with
a dumb-looking face, about my age

264
00:19:04,215 --> 00:19:06,911
and a big white haired old man
staying here?

265
00:19:07,252 --> 00:19:09,812
This is an inn for women only...

266
00:19:14,292 --> 00:19:15,657
I'm looking for someone...

267
00:19:15,727 --> 00:19:18,127
Do you have a blonde kid with
a dumb-looking face, about my age

268
00:19:18,196 --> 00:19:19,424
and a big white haired old man
staying here?

269
00:19:19,497 --> 00:19:21,055
Today, we only have old people.

270
00:19:27,005 --> 00:19:30,270
Hmm... this is kind of crisp
on the tongue...

271
00:19:36,681 --> 00:19:40,139
Hey, why are you guys all sleeping

272
00:19:40,885 --> 00:19:44,446
Do you have a blonde kid with
a dumb-looking face, about my age

273
00:19:44,522 --> 00:19:46,990
and a big white haired old man
staying here?

274
00:19:47,091 --> 00:19:48,353
White haired...?

275
00:19:48,426 --> 00:19:49,154
Are they here?!

276
00:19:49,527 --> 00:19:52,792
Eh... Do I remember seeing
some people like that earlier

277
00:19:52,864 --> 00:19:53,922
when shifts changed...?

278
00:19:55,500 --> 00:19:59,834
This tastes bitter...
are you all right with it? Cheers!

279
00:20:00,605 --> 00:20:03,802
Oh! A blond kid and
a white haired old man!

280
00:20:03,875 --> 00:20:06,002
They're here?!
What's their room number!

281
00:20:06,411 --> 00:20:08,379
Um...

282
00:20:08,446 --> 00:20:10,380
Room number one at
the end of the hallway

283
00:20:10,448 --> 00:20:11,745
on the second floor...

284
00:20:26,464 --> 00:20:30,025
What's up?
Has she already dumped you?

285
00:20:31,302 --> 00:20:33,133
Okay, Okay!

286
00:20:35,406 --> 00:20:38,136
Okay, Okay, I'll open up!

287
00:20:38,977 --> 00:20:40,069
Naruto!

288
00:20:45,116 --> 00:20:46,208
It's not him...

289
00:21:09,440 --> 00:21:13,376
<i>A cycle of hardship, right?</i>

290
00:21:14,378 --> 00:21:18,337
<i>Inside, we were crying, right?</i>

291
00:21:19,650 --> 00:21:27,614
<i>But the one thing we won't give up</i>
<i>is the dream we've chosen, right?</i>

292
00:21:28,592 --> 00:21:30,685
<i>It's a secondary role,</i>

293
00:21:33,464 --> 00:21:36,490
<i>a role in the shadows</i>

294
00:21:36,934 --> 00:21:41,871
<i>But in reaching for that dream,</i>

295
00:21:42,006 --> 00:21:47,467
<i>let us stay centered,</i>
<i>let us stay true</i>

296
00:21:47,745 --> 00:21:52,648
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we hung on without giving up</i>

297
00:21:52,717 --> 00:21:57,620
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we kept coming back up</i>

298
00:21:57,688 --> 00:22:06,858
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we believed and dreamed</i>

299
00:22:07,298 --> 00:22:12,201
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we've seen fools</i>

300
00:22:12,269 --> 00:22:18,105
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we've stood in the shadows of others</i>

301
00:22:19,744 --> 00:22:29,881
<i>Now, it's our turn...</i>
<i>Let us bask in our dreams</i>

302
00:22:37,528 --> 00:22:44,092
Darn it! My body is frozen!
What is this creepy feeling?

303
00:22:44,335 --> 00:22:47,031
This guy is absolutely not
an ordinary person.

304
00:22:47,705 --> 00:22:50,173
He's got the same Sharingan
as Sasuke.

305
00:22:50,241 --> 00:22:52,436
He's a member of Uchiha clan.

306
00:22:52,510 --> 00:22:57,641
Is this the guy Sasuke
was talking about?

307
00:22:58,716 --> 00:23:02,117
Next time: "Roar, Chidori!
Brother vs. Brother!"
